  "texts": [
    "They designed a multi-agent system with a blackboard-sharing module to address concurrency issues and improve task execution efficiency.",
    "On the other hand, synchronous collaboration systems provide real-time communication to support immediate response, enabling security analysts to exchange findings and divide tasks effectively.",
    "Thomas et al proposed a system that offers visualization, real-time communication, and efficient data processing to provide a comprehensive understanding of threats and corresponding response actions handled by multiple analysts.",
    "The recover function aims to ensure resilience planning and the timely restoration of capabilities or services that have been affected by a cybersecurity incident.",
    "Its primary objective is to quickly return to normal operations and minimize the impact of the incident, while also extracting valuable lessons learned."
